{"tid":1008083,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【豬年利是】滙豐派利是！逾兩萬員工各派500元","createTime":"2019-02-04T08:32:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-04T14:53:48.000Z","uid":227978,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"7e8034c6e60d8493fe0901738dd1c6a43d37d97e","tid":1008083,"uid":227978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T08:32:06.000Z","msg":"今天年三十晚，滙豐銀行提早向員工新增派發每人500元利是。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，該行早上已向員工發出內部通知，向在港工作逾兩萬名員工（包括長工及合約員工），各派500元電子利是，明天大年初一便會過數。<br />\n<br />\n滙豐發言人回覆傳媒查詢表示：「希望藉著農曆新年，感謝各同事過去一年的努力，因此，向每位香港員工派發500港元的電子利是，將會存入其出糧戶口。」<br />\n<br />\n據了解，以往滙豐過年後各部門只會派發開工利是20元，相信今年除了新增過年前500元利是外，過年後亦會繼續有部門開工利是。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E3%80%90%E8%B1%AC%E5%B9%B4%E5%88%A9%E6%98%AF%E3%80%91%E6%BB%99%E8%B1%90%E6%B4%BE%E5%88%A9%E6%98%AF%EF%BC%81%E9%80%BE%E5%85%A9%E8%90%AC%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E5%90%84%E6%B4%BE500%E5%85%83-052757225.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E8%25B1%25AC%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2588%25A9%25E6%2598%25AF%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%25BB%2599%25E8%25B1%2590%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E5%2588%25A9%25E6%2598%25AF%25EF%25BC%2581%25E9%2580%25BE%25E5%2585%25A9%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%2590%2584%25E6%25B4%25BE500%25E5%2585%2583-052757225.html&d=KChxWXaIVet3ZRtCu1MdJ5S3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=fdcbe9df\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E3%80%90%E8%B1%AC%E5%B9%B4%E5%88%A9%E6%98%AF%E3%80%91%E6%BB%99%E8%B1%90%E6%B4%BE%E5%88%A9%E6%98%AF%EF%BC%81%E9%80%BE%E5%85%A9%E8%90%AC%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E5%90%84%E6%B4%BE500%E5%85%83-052757225.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52568fd5a555bcb8fa79d1442b9dddd944a19ba5","tid":1008083,"uid":84282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T08:34:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"808a3ebe247ff8712bf4b759adad801dd34abbb2","tid":1008083,"uid":65743,"like":73,"dislike":0,"score":73,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-02-